column5: Some pics from Oct. Sorry, but I'm useless with a computer. Took a buddy and his wife out for the first time.They're hooked now. Rained most of the weekend but they just didn't care. They do look pleased though don't they? A weekend I won't soon forget. Chris.
Thanks for sharing.  Those are some nice fish.  Not sure which is bigger though, the smallies or the smilies!!! Great to hear you got to intoduce a couple of new people to fishing.
Thats some real nice fat fall smallies !!!!!!   some very happy fishermen there.....nice pics too,  thanks for sharing...cheers
WOW,and you dont even have a motor on the back of that boat.LOL  Real nice fish.
Some Really Nice Smallies! Great Report better late then never!
Congrats! Some  beauty fish and happy campers in there!
Dang things are pretty! LOL I liked fishing for them in October, no cooking in the boat, no bugs, getting a decent day on Lake Erie was a bit of a problem though.
Nice smallies and one Pike you slipped in
Actually, there is a trolling motor on the back, although I fished this lake for the first few yrs. with nothing but the oars. lol.  Chris.
